    <item>
      <title>受欢迎的对冲基金交易推动比特币期货空头创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/popular-hedge-fund-trade-pushes-bitcoin-futures-shorts-to-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杠杆基金对比特币期货的净空头持仓量创下历史新高，但不要误以为这是对冲基金的压倒性看跌情绪。这更可能是由于市场中性策略越来越受欢迎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/popular-hedge-fund-trade-pushes-bitcoin-futures-shorts-to-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
