      <title>美国因黄金调查对圭亚那富裕的穆罕默德家族实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-sanctions-guyana-s-wealthy-mohamed-family-on-gold-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部周二对纳扎尔·穆罕默德、他的儿子阿兹鲁丁及其公司穆罕默德企业实施制裁，原因是他们涉嫌在圭亚那参与公共腐败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-sanctions-guyana-s-wealthy-mohamed-family-on-gold-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
